snippet.title: Dual Eclipse - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3048300/Dual_Eclipse/
A first-person dungeon crawler that resolves turn-based combat with trick-taking. Parry cards, empower your deck, and explore dangerous dungeons.
